  "title": "Warehouse Asst @ Changi South",
  "description": "<h2>Job Duties</h2><ul><li><p>Receive, store, pick, pack, and load goods</p></li><li><p>Check items and quantities to make sure they are correct</p></li><li><p>Update stock records using a system or manual forms</p></li><li><p>Keep the warehouse clean, neat, and organized</p></li><li><p>Follow safety rules and wear safety equipment at all times</p></li><li><p>Report damaged items, missing stock, or safety issues to the supervisor</p></li><li><p>Help with stock counting when required</p></li><li><p>Do other warehouse tasks as assigned<br /></p></li></ul><h2>Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Experience in warehouse work is an advantage (training can be provided)</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a team</p></li><li><p>Responsible, hardworking, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Forklift license will be an added advantage</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Working hours (Fixed Shift)</strong><br />Morning shift: 8.00am to 5.45pm<br />Afternoon shift: 1.45pm - 11.30pm (shift allowance $10 per shift per day)<br />Night shift: 11.00pm - 8.45am (shift allowance $15 per shift per day)</p><p><strong>Work Days (Mon - Fri) OR (Thu - Mon), FIXED</strong><br /><strong>Working Location: Changi South(Co. tpt @ AMK, Woodlands, Pasir Ris and Seng Kang)</strong><br /></p><p>Liz Ooi Li Chen (R1104561)<br />Recruit Express Services Pte Ltd (13C6614)</p>",
